title: 3D-Printer
description: SLA uses a UV laser to solidify liquid resin layer by layer to create the object. It offers high-resolution printing and is commonly used in applications where high detail and smooth surface finish are required. | Printing Technology: FDM (Fused Deposition Modeling) | Large build volume: 400mm * 400mm * 450 mm | Print accuracy:0.05-0.3 mm | Positioning Accuracy: X/Y 0.0125mm，Z 0.0020mm | Extruder Quantity: Single | Nozzle Diameter: 0.4 mm Print Speed: 20~100mm/s | Materials: PLA, ABS, HIPS, Wood, TPU | Temperature Ambient Operating Temperature: 8ºC - 40ºC | Operational Extruder Temperature: max 260ºC | Software Input Formats: .STL, .OBJ, .JPG, PNG | Software Output Formats: GCode | Connectivity: Memory card; Data cable | Electrical Input rating: 110V/220V AC, 50/60Hz
variations: red | white | green | blue | black | orange | silver
